  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "a7e405e1b8828117531077bc89d930ce31ef88b09e9345d73d7409c41c63bfca": "Ah, yes; You must be [?]! Rat sent word that you would be coming. Everything is prepared. I have created a spell that will remove the mind control from the king.",
    "8b34817e862f3b110d83ff2cc800d713205610a8a4e588bd9c8740ce147edd6f": "What are you doing, [?]? I'm right here! Why are you trying to summon me again?",
    "5aca5af6397e6f250e4db1655583b4124e505c35dcb2730a900f29ecd2e67f10": "Thank you for your help, [?]. I will put the room back in order and then I must leave. Surok is defeated and will be no more trouble for us. We will guard him more closely from now on!",
    "316c560afcef8e0c94348f9aab635006c2ede78dd5675bc55c51138ee02bec2a": "Yes. You have done well, [?]. You are to be commended for your actions!",
    "e5e968d1a15ac1ead739dd5d5c6cb99b7007a1bab32ad6c29499c449419761b4": "There's still one in your inventory, [?]!",
    "d45d25e91e91c33f97fc334ad8e88a9146c49454e64a11cf881e39fd1b380c98": "Go and get the one that's in your bank, [?]!",
    "31c855b8c0a42f3f95650a8a4469907f7b1d8d11673343def9e14c2ac1b9b125": "Yes, of course, [?]. Here you are. Please bear in mind that this ring has no charges left with which to summon me, however."
  }
